{"tid":1824004,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家仲想唔想打落去？","createTime":"2020-01-14T06:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T08:41:29.000Z","uid":98542,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1798d0a9b2b8cdfe96791704105eb7a2049c8838","tid":1824004,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:26:14.000Z","msg":"我只想係度問三個問題：<br />\n<br />\n1. 香港法治制度仲係唔係有險可守？<br />\n<br />\n2. 以前話過呢次係endgame，點解依家冇人講？<br />\n<br />\n3. 由六月藍絲講呢次運動一定好快慘敗收場，到依家「遍地開花」，全世界都跟住我哋嗰套去做。去到今日，點解到今日身邊仲有人同我講「冇可能」？<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想係度引戰，我只係想問翻大家嘅初心去咗邊⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我知道呢段時間我哋失去左好多珍貴嘅嘢，甚至我哋身邊嘅手足，有唔少連區議會選舉大勝、成為社會大嘅嗰一刻都睇唔到。<br />\n<br />\n下面段片同埋佢套戲，我希望大家可以再重新睇多次，同埋問吓自己：我哋究竟想要一個點嘅香港？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/46OjIXuF1f4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F46OjIXuF1f4&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSernWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=59e87dea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/46OjIXuF1f4</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好再講「冇可能」，因為我去到今日呢一刻，我哋所做既都係由「冇可能」做起。<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港。"},{"pid":"f7480f9690f34a97033bfc7489cca837dce3afec","tid":1824004,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:28:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想多啲人參與行動？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">要記住嚟場革命唔係淨係屬於後生仔<br />\n四五十歲既人多數淨係上fb 佢地好多時都想參與行動 但又唔知有咩日程</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地有咩可以做？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1）我地要多啲<span style=\"color: red;\">係fb唔同post下面瘋狂洗版行動文宣</span><br />\n2）仲有要<span style=\"color: red;\">係街不斷airdrop啲文宣</span>俾人製造抗爭氣氛<br />\n3）隨身袋住啲文宣周街貼</strong></span><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔好淨係依賴文宣組<br />\n頭兩項都係零成本 <br />\n你唔係唔做呀嘛</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4637390c5c5c62265dcfa23c287c729dab8bb541","tid":1824004,"uid":131040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:33:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9b5df4020f8f2ac818e73e501b2b980f32be088","tid":1824004,"uid":98542,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:36:23.000Z","msg":"另外我想開一個「光復香港」既proposal，但我知道大家（包括我自己）唔想有大台，所以我想問過大家先出。大家想要嘅麻煩畀呢個回應正皮。"},{"pid":"261497dcaff0e87cd3b30075ac0fc3ecb4650172","tid":1824004,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:36:51.000Z","msg":"咁你想點<br />\n提高標準<br />\n學日本全共鬥搞死場運動？<br />\n咪巳經籌備緊工會搞罷工"},{"pid":"b710c8fbf60d017e0ba863cb5d6837ca92e893f1","tid":1824004,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"261497dcaff0e87cd3b30075ac0fc3ecb4650172","tid":1824004,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:36:51.000Z","msg":"咁你想點<br />\n提高標準<br />\n學日本全共鬥搞死場運動？<br />\n咪巳經籌備緊工會搞罷工"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:42:01.000Z","msg":"咁你覺得罷工可以令政府退到幾多？<br />\n一個訴求？一位手足？<br />\n睇嚟你唔知道另外四個訴求既價位係幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63349db312ab584a9e8d9d4f38aaa925e6dc86d","tid":1824004,"uid":240352,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:45:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4840ebc411ee3f70264a6d57ac4785d8a45b6db6","tid":1824004,"uid":304321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9euPGRP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9euPGRP.jpg&h=f251cb4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5258fa1c2c35ab08097077495373e8e668c3877","tid":1824004,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b710c8fbf60d017e0ba863cb5d6837ca92e893f1","tid":1824004,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"261497dcaff0e87cd3b30075ac0fc3ecb4650172","tid":1824004,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1